    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and refinement. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity remains uncompromised. Featuring a clean aesthetic and a smooth driving profile, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the driver seeking dependable quality and lasting value. Experience a vehicle that has been preserved with care and is prepared for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
