      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This driver\u2019s example delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed with a limited-slip differential providing excellent mid-corner traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a reinforced rear subframe and Vanos solenoid service to ensure long-term structural and mechanical reliability. While the aesthetics reflect honest road use, the powertrain and suspension geometry are dialed for peak performance. A purist-spec machine ready for the canyons.",
